trans-unit.source: Represents the data in a SOAP request sent or a SOAP response received by an XML Web service client at a specific <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer dataene i en SOAP-forespørselen som ble sendt eller svar SOAP mottatt av en XML-Web-tjenesteklienten på en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP request header field for the SOAP request or SOAP response.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP-forespørselen hodet felt for SOAP-forespørselen eller SOAP-svaret.

trans-unit.source: The Action property is available in any <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen er tilgjengelig i alle <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP request header field for the SOAP request or SOAP response.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP-forespørselen hodet felt for SOAP-forespørselen eller SOAP-svaret.

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the client proxy class, which derives from <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHttpClientProtocol"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en forekomst av klienten proxy-klassen som er avledet fra <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHttpClientProtocol"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The Client property can be accessed during any <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen klienten kan åpnes under noen <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>

trans-unit.source: An instance of the client proxy class.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av klienten proxy-klassen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a representation of the method prototype of the XML Web service method for which the SOAP request is intended.
trans-unit.target: Henter en representasjon av metoden prototypen i XML-Web service-metoden som SOAP-forespørselen er beregnet.

trans-unit.source: Although the MethodInfo property can be accessed during any stage, the method information is only available during <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.
trans-unit.target: Selv om egenskapen MethodInfo får under noen trinn, metoden informasjonen er bare tilgjengelig under <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> representing the XML Web service method for which the SOAP request is intended.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som representerer XML Web service-metoden som SOAP-forespørselen er beregnet.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the client waits for the server to finish processing an XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om klienten venter på serveren for å avslutte behandlingen av en XML-Web service-metode.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> applied to an XML Web service method or XML Web service client can specify whether the XML Web service method is one way by setting the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A> property of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute>brukes på en XML-Web service-metoden eller XML-tjenesteklienten kan angi om metoden XML Web service er én måte ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A>for attributtet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute.OneWay%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapRpcMethodAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapDocumentMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The OneWay property can be accessed during any <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen én vei kan åpnes under noen <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the client does not wait for the server to completely process a method.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis klienten ikke venter på at serveren behandler fullstendig metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the version of the SOAP protocol used to communicate with the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Henter versjonen av SOAP-protokollen som brukes til å kommunisere med XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: When an XML Web service supports SOAP version 1.1,.NET Framework clients communicate with an XML Web service in that version by default.
trans-unit.target: Når en XML-webtjeneste støtter SOAP versjon 1.1, kommunisere .NET Framework-klienter med en XML-webtjeneste i denne versjonen som standard.

trans-unit.source: For details on how to change the version of the SOAP protocol, see the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHttpClientProtocol.SoapVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du endrer versjonen av SOAP-protokollen, kan du se den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHttpClientProtocol.SoapVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHttpClientProtocol.SoapVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapProtocolVersion"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapProtocolVersion"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapProtocolVersion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapProtocolVersion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the URL of the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Henter URL-adresse for XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The Url property can be accessed during any <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.
trans-unit.target: URL-egenskapen kan åpnes under noen <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapMessageStage>

trans-unit.source: The URL of the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: URL-adresse for XML-webtjenesten.
